name: Unborn #1
description: This is a real image of an unborn fetus taken at OMSI in Portland, OR. There is something beautiful about the idea of existing, but never having to suffer the trials and tribulations of life. As of September 1, 2021, the state of Texas has enacted a new abortion restriction. Known as Senate Bill 8 (SB 8), this law limits the ability to provide abortion care in Texas beyond about 6 weeks of pregnancy, and sometimes even earlier.
